SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )
2024-04-02 09:41:42.993 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (13ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int64)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t."Id0", t."UserId", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId", t0."Id", t0."CreatedAt", t0."CreatedBy", t0."Description", t0."Name", t0."UpdatedAt", t0."UpdatedBy"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')

    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"

    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t."Id0", t."UserId", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId", t0."Id", t0."CreatedAt", t0."CreatedBy", t0."Description", t0."Name", t0."UpdatedAt", t0."UpdatedBy"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t."Id0", t."UserId", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId", t0."Id", t0."CreatedAt", t0."CreatedBy", t0."Description", t0."Name", t0."UpdatedAt", t0."UpdatedBy"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t."Id0", t."UserId", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId", t0."Id", t0."CreatedAt", t0."CreatedBy", t0."Description", t0."Name", t0."UpdatedAt", t0."UpdatedBy"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

2024-04-07 00:13:04.028 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (45ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND

            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid

                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace

                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')

2024-04-07 00:53:29.857 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (38ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace

                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'

                objid=cls.oid AND

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace

                objid=cls.oid AND

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

                    SELECT cls.oid

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions

            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace

                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND

        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'

                objid=cls.oid AND

    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"

) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t."Id0", t."UserId", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId", t0."Id", t0."CreatedAt", t0."CreatedBy", t0."Description", t0."Name", t0."UpdatedAt", t0."UpdatedBy"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy"

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

2024-04-07 23:29:32.546 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (38ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )
2024-04-07 23:29:32.809 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (11ms) [Parameters=[@__dto_Login_0='?'], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t0."RoleId", t0."UserId", t0."Id", t0."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "User" AS u
    WHERE u."Login" = @__dto_Login_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT u0."RoleId", u0."UserId", r."Id", r."Name"
    FROM "UserRole" AS u0
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS r ON u0."RoleId" = r."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."UserId"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t0."RoleId", t0."UserId", t0."Id", t0."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "User" AS u
    WHERE u."Id" = @__dto_UserId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT u0."RoleId", u0."UserId", r."Id", r."Name"
    FROM "UserRole" AS u0
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS r ON u0."RoleId" = r."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."UserId"

JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM (

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t0."RoleId", t0."UserId", t0."Id", t0."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "User" AS u
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT u0."RoleId", u0."UserId", r."Id", r."Name"
    FROM "UserRole" AS u0
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS r ON u0."RoleId" = r."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."UserId"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy"

    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

    SELECT u0."RoleId", u0."UserId", r."Id", r."Name"

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace

FROM pg_class AS cls

WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'

                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "User" AS u
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

    SELECT u0."RoleId", u0."UserId", r."Id", r."Name"
    FROM "UserRole" AS u0
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS r ON u0."RoleId" = r."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."UserId"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND

                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t."Id0", t."UserId", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId", t0."Id", t0."CreatedAt", t0."CreatedBy", t0."Description", t0."Name", t0."UpdatedAt", t0."UpdatedBy"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

FROM pg_class AS cls

        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

2024-04-09 21:13:49.891 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int64)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t."Id0", t."UserId", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId", t0."Id", t0."CreatedAt", t0."CreatedBy", t0."Description", t0."Name", t0."UpdatedAt", t0."UpdatedBy"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'

                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t."Id0", t."UserId", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId", t0."Id", t0."CreatedAt", t0."CreatedBy", t0."Description", t0."Name", t0."UpdatedAt", t0."UpdatedBy"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t

    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"

) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"

FROM pg_class AS cls

        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND

        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid

                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'

2024-04-09 21:24:07.690 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int64)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t."Id0", t."UserId", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId", t0."Id", t0."CreatedAt", t0."CreatedBy", t0."Description", t0."Name", t0."UpdatedAt", t0."UpdatedBy"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

                    SELECT cls.oid

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t0."RoleId", t0."UserId", t0."Id", t0."Name"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "User" AS u
    WHERE u."Login" = @__dto_Login_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT u0."RoleId", u0."UserId", r."Id", r."Name"
    FROM "UserRole" AS u0
    INNER JOIN "Role" AS r ON u0."RoleId" = r."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."UserId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."RoleId", t0."UserId"

2024-04-09 21:28:06.488 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (37ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM pg_class AS cls

WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND

                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t."Id0", t."UserId", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId", t0."Id", t0."CreatedAt", t0."CreatedBy", t0."Description", t0."Name", t0."UpdatedAt", t0."UpdatedBy"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t."Id0", t."UserId", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId", t0."Id", t0."CreatedAt", t0."CreatedBy", t0."Description", t0."Name", t0."UpdatedAt", t0."UpdatedBy"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

FROM pg_class AS cls

2024-04-09 22:03:33.616 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

                    SELECT cls.oid

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM pg_class AS cls

WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND

                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t."Id0", t."UserId", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId", t0."Id", t0."CreatedAt", t0."CreatedBy", t0."Description", t0."Name", t0."UpdatedAt", t0."UpdatedBy"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"

    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

    SELECT c."Id", c."UserId"
    FROM "Cart" AS c
    WHERE c."Id" = @__user_Cart_Id_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace

FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace

        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) = 0 THEN FALSE ELSE TRUE END
FROM pg_class AS cls
JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
WHERE
        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND
        ns.nspname NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND
        -- Exclude tables which are members of PG extensions
        NOT EXISTS (
            SELECT 1 FROM pg_depend WHERE
                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid
                    FROM pg_class AS cls
                             JOIN pg_namespace AS ns ON ns.oid = cls.relnamespace
                    WHERE relname='pg_class' AND ns.nspname='pg_catalog'
                ) AND
                objid=cls.oid AND
                deptype IN ('e', 'x')
        )

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t."Id0", t."UserId", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId", t0."Id", t0."CreatedAt", t0."CreatedBy", t0."Description", t0."Name", t0."UpdatedAt", t0."UpdatedBy"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"

2024-04-13 00:21:48.216 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int64)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t."Id0", t."UserId", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId", t0."Id", t0."CreatedAt", t0."CreatedBy", t0."Description", t0."Name", t0."UpdatedAt", t0."UpdatedBy"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"

FROM pg_class AS cls

        cls.relkind IN ('r', 'v', 'm', 'f', 'p') AND

                classid=(
                    SELECT cls.oid

SELECT t."Id", t."CreatedAt", t."CreatedBy", t."Login", t."Password", t."UpdatedAt", t."UpdatedBy", t."Id0", t."UserId", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId", t0."Id", t0."CreatedAt", t0."CreatedBy", t0."Description", t0."Name", t0."UpdatedAt", t0."UpdatedBy"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."CreatedBy", u."Login", u."Password", u."UpdatedAt", u."UpdatedBy", c."Id" AS "Id0", c."UserId"
    FROM "User" AS u
    LEFT JOIN "Cart" AS c ON u."Id" = c."UserId"
    WHERE u."Id" = @__p_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."CartId", c0."ProductId", p."Id", p."CreatedAt", p."CreatedBy", p."Description", p."Name", p."UpdatedAt", p."UpdatedBy"
    FROM "CartProduct" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Product" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS t0 ON t."Id0" = t0."CartId"
ORDER BY t."Id", t."Id0", t0."CartId", t0."ProductId"
